# By My Side 🐕

**An open-world survival-craft game about you and the dog at your side.**

[![Wishlist on Steam](https://img.shields.io/badge/Steam-Wishlist%20Now-blue?logo=steam)](https://store.steampowered.com/app/4859700/By_My_Side/)

> Survive the wild with a loyal dog at your side. Wash up with nothing, tame a stray and raise it as your companion — build and power a home, outlast brutal winters, and face a world that fights back.

---

## 🎮 About

You wash up alone in the wilderness — nothing but your hands and what the land gives you. You chop wood, raise a shelter, and fight to stay alive as the seasons turn toward a merciless winter. Then one day, a stray dog crosses your path. Feed it. Earn its trust. Watch it grow — and it never leaves your side.

**By My Side** is an open-world survival-craft game about raw survival, a home you build with your own hands, and the bond that grows between you and your dog.

## ✨ Features

- **🐕 Your Dog, Your Story** — Find a stray and raise it from a pup. Each run brings a different breed with its own look and talent. Teach it tricks, put it to work — guard, hunt, or haul a sled.
- **🏡 Build & Power a Home** — From a first campfire to a walled homestead with a glass greenhouse. Build a full power-and-water grid: solar, batteries, pumps, heaters, sprinklers and smart-relay automation.
- **🔨 Craft Everything** — Over 90 recipes across workbench, furnace, campfire and powered machines, with real multi-step crafting trees.
- **❄️ Survive the Seasons** — Stay warm, fed and dry as the seasons turn toward a winter that wants you dead.
- **🌾 Live Off the Land** — Farm crops, raise animals, trade with a wandering merchant, and automate the grind.
- **🐺 Defend What's Yours** — Read the danger, fortify your home, and hold the line against wolf-pack sieges.
- **🧭 Every Run Is Different** — A dozen origins, each with a real strength and weakness.
- **🎮 Two Ways to Play** — Survival (hardcore, permadeath) or Story (relaxed building).

## 🌍 Languages

